## Help file for --generate ## 
usage : ./run.sh [file=...] [fdate=...] [dur=...]

file : filepath of the output file. Set at "data/historic.csv" buy default.

fdate : first date of the historic. Set by default today at 9am.
The last date of the historic is calculate with the first date + the duration
### Note: ### the opening and closing time are set at the current opening and starting hours of the Paris stock market.
#### from 9am to 5:30pm ####

dur : the duration of the simulation in days. Set by default at 7 days.
By default, the program generate a price each 5s. So total point generate := duration * (closing_hour_in_s - opening_hour_in_s ) / 5

